    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1924-01-23T17:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1924-01-23T17:00:00-05:00" n="343"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d343">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">812.00/26844: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Consul at Vera Cruz</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wood</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1924-01-23T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 23, 1924—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Report immediately when all mines have been removed from ports mentioned in your
                    January 23, 9 a.m.; also ascertain whether there <pb facs="0530" n="436"
                        xml:id="pg_436"/> are any other ports where mines have been placed and if
                    so, whether these will also be removed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
